@page "/benefits"

<Banner
        Title="Benefits"
        SubTitle="Your health and well-being are crucial to our collective success.
                <br/> Learn more about the top-rated benefits Uju employees enjoy."
        BackgroundPath="/img/benefits/BenefitsAtUJU.jpg"
    />

                <div class="container">
                    <div class="my-5 mx-auto text-center">
                        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bolder">Comprehensive healthcare</h1>
                        <h1 class="fs-5 text-muted">
                            We take wellness to heart and strive to keep our teams happy and healthy in all they do, now and in the future.
                        </h1>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-4 mb-3 text-center" style="max-width: 80vw; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <div class="col d-flex">
                            <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column" style="min-height: 250px; background-color:#F7F7F7">
                                <div class="card-body flex-grow-1">
                                    <h4 class="my-0 fw-bold mb-3">Medical</h4>
                                    Uju provides access to a multitude of
                                    medical plans which all include prescription
                                    coverage and wellness resources to keep you
                                    balanced.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col d-flex">
                            <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column" style="min-height: 250px; background-color:#F7F7F7">
                                <div class="card-body flex-grow-1">
                                    <h4 class="my-0 fw-bold mb-3">Dental</h4>
                                    Flexibility is a key feature of our dental plans,
                                    giving you the freedom to choose from a long
                                    roster of dentists.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col d-flex">
                            <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column" style="min-height: 250px; background-color:#F7F7F7">
                                <div class="card-body flex-grow-1">
                                    <h4 class="my-0 fw-bold mb-3">Paid Time Off</h4>
                                    We offer a generous PTO policy that allows all
                                    regular, full-time employees to accrue the
                                    equivalent of 20 days per year, increasing with
                                    tenure, in addition to company holidays.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col d-flex">
                            <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column" style="min-height: 250px; background-color:#F7F7F7">
                                <div class="card-body flex-grow-1">
                                    <h4 class="my-0 fw-bold mb-3">Family Care</h4>
                                    Our people and their families receive
                                    world-class therapeutic services and support
                                    through our health network.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="featurette-divider">

                    <div class="my-5 mx-auto text-center">
                        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bolder">Work Life Success</h1>
                        <h1 class="fs-5 text-muted">
                            Balance is the key to sustainable innovation. With Work Life Success, we strive to help you synchronize work and personal life.
                        </h1>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row d-flex align-items-center gx-5">
                        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                            <img src="/img/benefits/Celebrating.jpg" alt="Description of image" class="img-fluid" style="min-height:500px; width:auto; object-fit:cover;">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                            <p class="lead">
                                At Uju, we believe that supporting our employees’ overall wellbeing drives innovation and business success.
                                <br /><br />That’s why we offer a robust Work Life Excellence program that promotes growth both in and out of the office.
                                <br /><br />Our RECHARGE rooms provide quiet spaces to meditate or nap when you need a break in the workday.
                                <br /><br />We incentivize community service with our Care For Others volunteer program, matching your service hours with donations to the cause.
                                <br /><br />Our WORKOUT benefit provides an annual stipend towards fitness activities and equipment to encourage both physical and mental health.
                                <br /><br />At Uju, we strive to create a supportive, nourishing environment so our team can do their best work while also pursuing personal growth and joy.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                </div>

<Footer />